title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Unexpected changes on the home front likely catch you off guard now. For example, your partner or roommate might suddenly rearrange the living room. Or, an essential appliance could go on the fritz at a critical time as the nurturing Moon crashes into unpredictable Uranus in your 4th House of Domestic Conditions. Although your residence may not seem like paradise with so many abrupt adjustments, you can still adapt to the situations if you keep an open and creative mind. Remember, most disruptions today are temporary. A Swedish proverb teaches, Worry often gives a small thing a big shadow. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
